{"tid":891881,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【冇圖】後生仔女得閒就應該入啲屋邨公園望下班廢老","createTime":"2018-11-06T12:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T16:08:18.000Z","uid":14797,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8c59cee723260ca66acec72de1e7190657915beb","tid":891881,"uid":14797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T12:45:44.000Z","msg":"有活力有精力嗰堆唔計<br />\n<br />\n講緊係日日無所事事望天打掛<br />\n毫無生氣可言嗰班廢中廢老<br />\n有啲一睇就知有病<br />\n有啲望落都正正常常不過就成個空殼咁<br />\n講得難聽啲好似日日坐喺度等唔知幾時死咁<br />\n<br />\n唔係歧視老人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老人都可以好精靈<br />\n但呢班廢老就真係不了<br />\n<br />\n再問下自己幾十年後想唔想變成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學業 事業 健康 襯而家仲有能力就好好努力<br />\n我諗上得連登睇得呢個post嘅巴絲就算年紀再大 相比之下都仲有時間去努力掙扎<br />\n自己諗清楚啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係冇圖，自己得閒去行返轉感受下"},{"pid":"e071346e0ea0b2b2f3f60cb472446b214ce65342","tid":891881,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T12:46:05.000Z","msg":"OK"},{"pid":"6b25e39bb6dcaa5f7bdb6594b13209e351d5f61a","tid":891881,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e071346e0ea0b2b2f3f60cb472446b214ce65342","tid":891881,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T12:46:05.000Z","msg":"OK"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T12:53:35.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"fecaed06d842bcc2b06a14e4aa09ad389321c417","tid":891881,"uid":14797,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:06:35.000Z","msg":"歡迎廢老俾負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909f4eb62e256c3e2d1e6b1d17a29800a629b5bb","tid":891881,"uid":154664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:09:56.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"1c1621c0f77f7556f7ee9c8a23701dd7461e9855","tid":891881,"uid":210944,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:20:34.000Z","msg":"我明你意思<br />\n一把年紀 但又冇成就又人理<br />\n惟一貢獻就係娶個北姑上嚟<img src