>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:33:03.000Z","msg":"反話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2915a27484b2cb16f036960c81a682e50db56c","tid":891881,"uid":212125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:46:08.000Z","msg":"有活力有精力嗰班唔計你玩撚哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個世界個個都有錢人嚟㗎 不過窮同埋低下階層唔計有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593d5b780da0187f5c113e1ac34dca88311a39ca","tid":891881,"uid":14797,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:47:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔係仇視廢老</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能有部分人年輕時生活得唔好<br />\n人生冇乜娛樂興趣<br />\n老咗冇工作就唔知自己可以做乜<br />\n日日坐喺度等死變咗廢老 其實幾悲哀<br />\n<br />\n只係想勸諭大家要警惕自己唔好變成咁<br />\n老人一樣可以有好多活動<br />\n琴棋書畫運動影相跳舞甚至有能力嘅仲可以工作<br />\n<br />\n相反 後生時唔諗呢啲嘢<br />\n仲鳩下鳩下咁過每一日<br />\n未來坐喺長櫈俾人望嗰個就係你"},{"pid":"8d5a8d4faee0b2087ae7e33f7745877617775308","tid":891881,"uid":14797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}